---
title: Creamy Mushroom Spaghetti With Burrata plus Lemony Toasted Panko
description: A topping of rich burrata cheese brings a luxuriously creamy texture to spaghetti tossed in savory mushroom sauce with scallions and freshly squeezed lemon juice. Sprinkle golden lemony toasted breadcrumbs over the top just before serving for a bright finale to this restaurant-inspired pasta bowl.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66a7cf66ff70d218deffb2e8-3900f57a.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66a7cf66ff70d218deffb2e8-en-US.pdf
course: main course
cuisine: Southern Europe
author: HelloFresh
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 810 kcal
  fat: 45 g
  saturated fat: 23 g
  carbohydrates: 79 g
  sugar: 6 g
  protein: 21 g
  fiber: 6 g
